'''NBA全明星名人赛'''（{{lang-en|NBA All-Star Celebrity Game}}）是[[NBA|NBA]]的一项年度表演篮球赛，是[[NBA全明星周末|NBA全明星周末]]的一部分。参加这项篮球赛的球员通常是退役的NBA和[[WNBA|WNBA]]篮球明星、演员、歌手以及其他职业联盟的明星运动员。首届名人赛举办于2002-03赛季的亚特兰大全明星周末。一般该赛事在全明星周末的周五晚上进行。<ref>{{Cite news | author = Corey Moss | url = http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1485103/20040217/nelly.jhtml | title = Paris, P. Diddy Help Make NBA All-Star Game An Afterthought | work = MTV | date = 2004-02-17 | accessdate = 2021-03-13 | archive-date = 2009-02-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090218010911/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1485103/20040217/nelly.jhtml | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>"{{Cite news | url = http://www.azcentral.com/sports/suns/allstar/articles/2008/12/17/20081217nbaallstar1218.html | title = All-Star even tickets for sale Friday | work = The Arizona Republic | date = 2008-12-17| accessdate = 2021-03-13}}</ref>不过，有时该赛事在全明星周末的训练场馆，而非全明星正赛的场馆进行。

